  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b8663018083e44059281731f5b6e58c0, type: 3}
  m_Name: Line_S4_Narration_03
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Bonbibi.DialogueLine
  speaker: 0
  text: Dokkhin Rai stands at the treeline. He is enormous and completely still.
    He is not looking at Dhona's retreating boats. He is not hunting you. He is simply
    standing where the forest ends and the river begins, and his eyes are on you
    because you are what is left.
